OpenHAB cloud secure remote access


Master user:

0.) Register account in the https://myopenhab.org

1.) Add users by email and password ( each user has their own password)





Regular user:

0.) go to https://myopenhab.org and sign in with your email and password





Mobile oenHAB app: Setting -> cancel Demo check box -> 	Local URL: 	http:server_ip:8080
	Remote URL: 	https:myopenhab.org -> your password
-> select the sitemap
